                            <comment id="15484115" author="caomanhdat" created="Mon, 12 Sep 2016 13:26:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Initial patch for this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15487416" author="shalinmangar" created="Tue, 13 Sep 2016 14:53:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Dat. A few comments:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Thread.sleep should move to end of the loop instead of the start. This is so that the first iteration doesn&apos;t sleep unnecessarily.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The DocCollection variable is named &quot;clusterProps&quot;. Cluster props indicate that this is a cluster property but it is not. It should be called collection instead.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The &quot;isEquals&quot; doesn&apos;t indicate its purpose very well. Perhaps better to rename it as &quot;isCollectionModified&quot; or maybe &quot;areChangesVisible&quot;?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</comment>
